snippet.title: Guilty Gear -Strive- - Millia and Zato Gameplay Footage
snippet.description:
Exclusive Millia and Zato gameplay footage!

Guilty Gear -Strive-, the latest entry in the groundbreaking fighting game series from Arc System Works, is coming to the PlayStation®4 Early 2021 with new gameplay, characters, and innovative rollback net code. 

Coming Early 2021!

For more info, visit https://www.arcsystemworks.jp/guiltygear/en/
Also be sure to follow us on Twitter @ArcSystemWorksU
